title: California Governor Brown Signs Bill Ensuring Patient Access to Interchangeable Biologic Medicines
text: WASHINGTON--(BUSINESS WIRE)--The Biotechnology Industry Organization commends California Governor Jerry Brown for signing critical legislation to create a pathway for the substitution of interchangeable biologic medicines. ...
